<p><strong>Principal Investigator (PI) and Lead Organization:</strong><br />
Dr. Fangxing (Fran) Li, James W. McConnell Professor &amp; IEEE Fellow, University of Tennessee, Knoxville</p>

<p><strong>Co-PIs:</strong><br />
